{"tid":2418071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁君彥形容首批接種疫苗議員「義勇軍」及「白老鼠」","createTime":"2021-02-22T10:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T11:01:20.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db89e7f800c5f472517b6f8129ff03bfbfe7f076","tid":2418071,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1576850_1_20210222184008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1576850_1_20210222184008.jpg&h=83ccf81a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁君彥稱議員接種疫苗能夠向市民證明疫苗是安全，值得安心信賴。（李錦華攝）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥表示，同事對接種疫苗有不同意見，有議員想盡早接種，亦有議員持反對意見。早前已10多名議員因兼任人大政協，已接種國產疫苗，亦有數位行會成員已接種。他形容，首批接種疫苗的是議員「義勇軍」和「白老鼠」，能夠向市民證明疫苗是安全，值得安心信賴，並呼籲市民為己為人，早日登記接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼表示，今次率先接種疫苗是支持國產疫苗的行動，非常感謝中央政府短時間安排100萬劑疫苗，亦呼籲市民網上登記，同時建議政府放寬其他群組，讓更多市民接種，以達至群體免疫。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576850-20210222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576850-20210222.htm&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XuoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=fdc58279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576850-20210222.htm&h=efd172f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576850-20210222.htm</a>"},{"pid":"db662b56a83083333f796ce2fe1cb9413ab9eb3d","tid":2418071,"uid":7369,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:43:09.000Z","msg":"就算冇副作用都戇鳩啦，得50%仲要世衞都唔認可！"},{"pid":"4dfe0ecee90a059e97102c4cfb8e0dfdaf612490","tid":2418071,"uid":99962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"梁美芬點睇都係黑"},{"pid":"cbee1ff877364c73494e857f9000c5b2030f54a9","tid":2418071,"uid":18251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"又唔係打科興白咩老鼠呀"},{"pid":"fe